OL,5, People need to be 'less squeamish'     
OL,6, about drinking water taken from sewage 
OL,7, treatment plants, the head of the      
OL,8, Environment Agency has said.           
OL,10,FWater companies are planning           
OL,11,F"toilet-to-tap" systems, also known as 
OL,12,Fwater recycling, to turn sewage from   
OL,13,Flavatories into drinking water by      
OL,14,Ftreating it.                           
OL,16,FBy 2030, toilet water could be         
OL,17,Fdeposited into rivers near treatment   
OL,18,Fplants so it can be collected and      
OL,19,Fprocessed as drinking water.           
